Corrosion Specialist
Corrosion Specialist
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  negotiableAmoria Bond is pleased to offer a unique opportunity within a well-reputed, multinational Oil & Gas company who requires a Corrosion Specialist. This role will be primarily based in Singapore on a permanent basis.
The successful candidate will have a minimum of 8 years of experience within the Oil and Gas industry and a career background focused on asset integrity management, pipeline integrity management, coating and corrosion protection and good knowledge on corrosion analysis.
One of the key functions of the role will be executing projects related to maintenance and inspection planning, root cause analysis and planning laboratory services. If you are motivated towards developing a real specialism in respect to corrosion and is interested to develop a competence in materials technology, then this opportunity is definitely something to seriously take a look at.
Salaries will be dependent on skill set and experience but will be competitive.
If you are available immediately and would like further information on this role please forward your CV for immediate consideration to charlotte . chicv @ amoriabond . com
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
